### Day 6: create a coding conversation and store its id for following requests
POST http://localhost:8080/api/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Java debugging session"
}

> {% client.global.set("codingConversationId", response.body.id); %}

### Day 6: send a message in the created conversation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "请帮我分析这段 Java 代码的 bug",
  "conversationId": "{{codingConversationId}}"
}

### Day 6: inspect the stored user message, answer, and route metadata
GET http://localhost:8080/api/conversations/{{codingConversationId}}/messages

### Day 6: list all conversations ordered by latest activity
GET http://localhost:8080/api/conversations

### Day 6: create an isolated daily-planning conversation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Daily planning test"
}

> {% client.global.set("dailyConversationId", response.body.id); %}

### Day 6: first daily request, constrained to one sentence
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "请用一句话为我制定明天上午的学习计划。",
  "conversationId": "{{dailyConversationId}}"
}

### Day 6: follow up in the same conversation, also constrained to one sentence
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "请用一句话总结上面的讨论。",
  "conversationId": "{{dailyConversationId}}"
}

### Day 9: propose a manual file creation without changing the file yet
POST http://localhost:8080/api/file-operations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rootId": "agent-workspace",
  "operationType": "CREATE_FILE",
  "targetPath": "nested/day9-manual.txt",
  "content": "This content must appear only after approval.",
  "approvalMode": "MANUAL"
}

> {% client.global.set("manualFileOperationId", response.body.operationId); %}

### Day 9: list pending operations and verify the proposal is awaiting approval
GET http://localhost:8080/api/file-operations?status=PENDING

### Day 9: approve the pending operation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/file-operations/{{manualFileOperationId}}/approve

### Day 9: verify that approval created the file
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/content?path=nested/day9-manual.txt

### Day 9: roll back the approved creation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/file-operations/{{manualFileOperationId}}/rollback

### Day 9: propose an operation that will be rejected
POST http://localhost:8080/api/file-operations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rootId": "agent-workspace",
  "operationType": "CREATE_FILE",
  "targetPath": "nested/day9-rejected.txt",
  "content": "This file must never be created.",
  "approvalMode": "MANUAL"
}

> {% client.global.set("rejectedFileOperationId", response.body.operationId); %}

### Day 9: reject the operation without touching the file system
POST http://localhost:8080/api/file-operations/{{rejectedFileOperationId}}/reject

### Day 9: full-access mode approves and executes immediately
POST http://localhost:8080/api/file-operations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rootId": "agent-workspace",
  "operationType": "CREATE_FILE",
  "targetPath": "nested/day9-full-access.txt",
  "content": "Full access executes this proposal immediately.",
  "approvalMode": "FULL_ACCESS"
}

### Day 9: verify the full-access file exists
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/content?path=nested/day9-full-access.txt

### Day 9: roll back the most recently executed operation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/file-operations/rollback-last

### Day 9: inspect the latest audit records and statuses
GET http://localhost:8080/api/file-operations

### Day 8: create a temporary test directory
POST http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/directories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "nested/day8-test"
}

### Day 8: create a text file without overwriting existing files
POST http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/files
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "nested/day8-test/draft.txt",
  "content": "Day 8 first version"
}

### Day 8: update the text file using atomic replacement
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/content
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "nested/day8-test/draft.txt",
  "content": "Day 8 updated version"
}

### Day 8: rename the updated file
POST http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/rename
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourcePath": "nested/day8-test/draft.txt",
  "targetPath": "nested/day8-test/final.txt"
}

### Day 8: verify the renamed file content
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/content?path=nested/day8-test/final.txt

### Day 8: list the temporary directory
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/entries?path=nested/day8-test

### Day 8: delete the test file
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace?path=nested/day8-test/final.txt

### Day 8: delete the now-empty test directory
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace?path=nested/day8-test

### Day 8: write traversal must be rejected with 403
POST http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/files
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "../blocked.txt",
  "content": "This file must never be created"
}

### Day 7: create an isolated conversation for real Demo.java analysis
POST http://localhost:8080/api/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Real Demo.java analysis"
}

> {% client.global.set("demoAnalysisConversationId", response.body.id); %}

### Day 7: read Demo.java and build the model request dynamically
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/content?path=nested/Demo.java

> {%
    client.global.set("demoAnalysisRequest", JSON.stringify({
        question: "请分析下面的 Java 源代码，指出导致运行时异常的代码行、异常原因和最小修复方案；请控制在三句话内。\n\n" + response.body.content,
        conversationId: client.global.get("demoAnalysisConversationId")
    }));
%}

### Day 7: send the loaded Demo.java to the configured real coding model
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{{demoAnalysisRequest}}

### Day 7: verify that the file-analysis conversation stores the request and answer
GET http://localhost:8080/api/conversations/{{demoAnalysisConversationId}}/messages

### Day 6: verify that the daily conversation contains four messages
GET http://localhost:8080/api/conversations/{{dailyConversationId}}/messages

### Day 7: list configured file roots
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/roots

### Day 7: list files in the nested workspace
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/entries?path=nested

### Day 7: read the nested Markdown test file
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/content?path=nested/todo.md

### Day 7: read the nested text test file
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/content?path=nested/notes.txt

### Day 7: read the nested Java test file
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/content?path=nested/Demo.java

### Day 7: path traversal must be rejected with 403
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/agent-workspace/content?path=../model-route-agent/pom.xml


### Day 6: summarize the coding conversation with the configured general model
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "请用一句话总结上面的讨论。",
  "conversationId": "{{dailyConversationId}}"
}
